    <item>
      <title>Teaching</title>
      <link>https://thomasbury.net/teaching/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Dec 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://thomasbury.net/teaching/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;workshop-on-interactive-data-visualisation-in-python&#34;&gt;Workshop on interactive data visualisation in Python&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a workshop I have given for various institutions including the Centre de Recherches Mathématiques, the Centre for Applied Mathematics in Bioscience and Medicine, and the Quantitative Life Sciences Dept. at McGill University. Slides and Jupyter notebooks are available at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ThomasMBury/workshop_datavis_python&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Github repository&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;qlsc-600-resetting-and-entraining-biological-oscillators-mcgill&#34;&gt;QLSC 600, Resetting and Entraining Biological Oscillators, McGill&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
  &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download  pr-1 fa-fw&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/qls600/module1_outline.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Course outline&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bootcamp on nonlinear dynamics (&lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/qls600/nonlinear_bootcamp.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;slides&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Early warning signals for bifurcations (&lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/qls600/ews_slides.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;slides&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/qls600/ews_practice.ipynb.zip&#34;&gt;Jupyter notebook&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cardiac arrhythmia (&lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/qls600/cardiac_arrhythmia.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;slides&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;math-127-calculus-i-for-the-sciences-uwat&#34;&gt;Math 127, Calculus I for the Sciences, UWat&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
  &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download  pr-1 fa-fw&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/math127/math127_lecs.zip&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Lecture notes (handwritten)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
