  &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download  pr-1 fa-fw&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://thomasbury.net/uploads/math117/examples_9.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Improper Integrals, Polar Coordinates and Complex Numbers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;amath-777-stochastic-processes-in-the-physical-sciences-uwat&#34;&gt;AMATH 777, Stochastic Processes in the Physical Sciences, UWat&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
